{"title":"Acid blast (monster spell)","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Acid_blast_(monster_spell)","type":"markdown","data":"**Acid blast** is a [monster spell](/wiki/Monster_spell \"Monster spell\") that appears in [EvilHack](/wiki/EvilHack \"EvilHack\") and [Hack'EM](/wiki/Hack%27EM \"Hack'EM\"), and functions similarly to the [spell of acid blast](/wiki/Spell_of_acid_blast \"Spell of acid blast\").\n\n## Description\n\nAcid blast can be used by any monster that can cast mage spells and is at least [level](/wiki/Monster_level \"Monster level\") 15. When cast, the caster will target a monster that they can see (or the square where they believe that monster to be) with a 3x3 explosion of acid centered on that square; if successful, the explosion can corrode unprotected [armor](/wiki/Armor \"Armor\") and [wielded](/wiki/Wield \"Wield\") [weapons](/wiki/Weapon \"Weapon\") in the open inventory of any monsters caught within. The spell can miss the monster and blast the floor or ceiling harmlessly, and will have no effect if the target has complete [acid resistance](/wiki/Acid_resistance \"Acid resistance\").\n\nMonsters will not use this spell against a monster that is peaceful and not subject to a [grudge](/wiki/Grudge \"Grudge\"), or else one they know to have acid resistance. Monsters will also avoid using the spell if they are not aware of an appropriate target, would be caught in their own blast, or else they would target you while you have [invulnerability](/wiki/Invulnerability \"Invulnerability\"), e.g. from a successful [prayer](/wiki/Prayer \"Prayer\").\n\n## Strategy\n\nThe acid blast spell makes acid resistance a necessity in the late game, as a successful hit can burn through a chunk of a character's HP: acid resistance can only be obtained extrinsically, making it important to have room in a character build for the property when planning to face specific monsters such as [Kathryn the Ice Queen](/wiki/Kathryn_the_Ice_Queen \"Kathryn the Ice Queen\"), even on a temporary basis.\n\n## Messages\n\n- \\<The monster> douses you in a torrent of acid!\n\n  A monster cast the acid blast spell at you and hit you.\n\n- The acid dissipates harmlessly.\n\n  As above, but you have acid resistance.\n\n- \\<The monster> blasts the \\<floor/ceiling> with acid and curses!\n\n  You saw a monster cast the acid blast spell at you, but the spell missed.\n\n* *This page is a **[stub](/wiki/Category:Stubs \"Category:Stubs\")**. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by [**expanding this page**.](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Acid_blast_\\(monster_spell\\)\\&action=edit)*\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Acid blast (monster spell) - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Acid_blast_(monster_spell)\",\"wgTitle\":\"Acid blast (monster spell)\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":160091,\"wgRevisionId\":160091,\"wgArticleId\":39005,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Stubs\",\"EvilHack monster spells\",\"Hack'EM monster spells\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Acid_blast_(monster_spell)\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":39005,\"wgRequestId\":\"8ec80276d2a683156fe8b992\",\"wgCSPNonce\":false,\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[],\"wgWikiEditorEnabledModules\":[],\"wgCategoryTreePageCategoryOptions\":\"{\\\"mode\\\":0,\\\"hideprefix\\\":20,\\\"showcount\\\":true,\\\"namespaces\\\":false}\"});mw.loader.state({\"site.styles\":\"ready\",\"noscript\":\"ready\",\"user.styles\":\"ready\",\"user\":\"ready\",\"user.options\":\"ready\",\"user.tokens\":\"loading\",\"mediawiki.legacy.shared\":\"ready\",\"mediawiki.legacy.commonPrint\":\"ready\",\"mediawiki.skinning.interface\":\"ready\",\"skins.vector.styles\":\"ready\"});mw.loader.implement(\"user.tokens@0tffind\",function($,jQuery,require,module){/*@nomin*/mw.user.tokens.set({\"editToken\":\"+\\\\\",\"patrolToken\":\"+\\\\\",\"watchToken\":\"+\\\\\",\"csrfToken\":\"+\\\\\"});\n});RLPAGEMODULES=[\"site\",\"mediawiki.page.startup\",\"mediawiki.user\",\"mediawiki.page.ready\",\"mediawiki.searchSuggest\",\"skins.vector.js\"];mw.loader.load(RLPAGEMODULES);});</script>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=mediawiki.legacy.commonPrint%2Cshared%7Cmediawiki.skinning.interface%7Cskins.vector.styles&amp;only=styles&amp;skin=vector\"/>\n<script async=\"\" src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=startup&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector\"></script>\n<meta name=\"ResourceLoaderDynamicStyles\" content=\"\"/>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=site.styles&amp;only=styles&amp;skin=vector\"/>\n<meta name=\"generator\" content=\"MediaWiki 1.32.5\"/>\n<link rel=\"image_src\" href=\"/images/6/65/Nethackwiki-logo.png\"/>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/images/6/64/Favicon.ico\"/>\n<link rel=\"search\" type=\"application/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"NetHackWiki\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/wiki/Acid_blast_(monster_spell)\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Acid_blast_monster_spell rootpage-Acid_blast_monster_spell skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Acid blast (monster spell)</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Acid blast</b> is a <a href=\"/wiki/Monster_spell\" title=\"Monster spell\">monster spell</a> that appears in <a href=\"/wiki/EvilHack\" title=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Hack%27EM\" title=\"Hack&#39;EM\">Hack'EM</a>, and functions similarly to the <a href=\"/wiki/Spell_of_acid_blast\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Spell of acid blast\">spell of acid blast</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Description\">Description</span></h2>\n<p>Acid blast can be used by any monster that can cast mage spells and is at least <a href=\"/wiki/Monster_level\" title=\"Monster level\">level</a> 15. When cast, the caster will target a monster that they can see (or the square where they believe that monster to be) with a 3x3 explosion of acid centered on that square; if successful, the explosion can corrode unprotected <a href=\"/wiki/Armor\" title=\"Armor\">armor</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Wield\" title=\"Wield\">wielded</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Weapon\" title=\"Weapon\">weapons</a> in the open inventory of any monsters caught within. The spell can miss the monster and blast the floor or ceiling harmlessly, and will have no effect if the target has complete <a href=\"/wiki/Acid_resistance\" title=\"Acid resistance\">acid resistance</a>.\n</p><p>Monsters will not use this spell against a monster that is peaceful and not subject to a <a href=\"/wiki/Grudge\" title=\"Grudge\">grudge</a>, or else one they know to have acid resistance. Monsters will also avoid using the spell if they are not aware of an appropriate target, would be caught in their own blast, or else they would target you while you have <a href=\"/wiki/Invulnerability\" title=\"Invulnerability\">invulnerability</a>, e.g. from a successful <a href=\"/wiki/Prayer\" title=\"Prayer\">prayer</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Strategy\">Strategy</span></h2>\n<p>The acid blast spell makes acid resistance a necessity in the late game, as a successful hit can burn through a chunk of a character's HP: acid resistance can only be obtained extrinsically, making it important to have room in a character build for the property when planning to face specific monsters such as <a href=\"/wiki/Kathryn_the_Ice_Queen\" title=\"Kathryn the Ice Queen\">Kathryn the Ice Queen</a>, even on a temporary basis.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Messages\">Messages</span></h2>\n<dl><dt><span id=\"douses_you_in_a_torrent_of_acid.21\">&lt;The monster&gt; douses you in a torrent of acid!</span></dt>\n<dd>A monster cast the acid blast spell at you and hit you.</dd>\n<dt><span id=\"The_acid_dissipates_harmlessly.\">The acid dissipates harmlessly.</span></dt>\n<dd>As above, but you have acid resistance.</dd>\n<dt><span id=\"blasts_the_with_acid_and_curses.21\">&lt;The monster&gt; blasts the &lt;floor/ceiling&gt; with acid and curses!</span></dt>\n<dd>You saw a monster cast the acid blast spell at you, but the spell missed.</dd></dl>\n<div class=\"stub\">\n<dl><dd><i>This page is a <b><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Stubs\" title=\"Category:Stubs\">stub</a></b>. Should you wish to do so, you can contribute by <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Acid_blast_(monster_spell)&amp;action=edit\"><b>expanding this page</b>.</a></i></dd></dl>\n</div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926182214\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 77/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 277/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1103/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 788/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 6/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.274      1 -total\n 66.70%    3.518      3 Template:Message\n 29.77%    1.570      1 Template:Stub\n 28.63%    1.510      3 Template:Pp\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:39005-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926182214 and revision id 160091\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Acid_blast_(monster_spell)&amp;oldid=160091\">https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Acid_blast_(monster_spell)&amp;oldid=160091</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Categories\" title=\"Special:Categories\">Categories</a>: <ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Category:Stubs\" title=\"Category:Stubs\">Stubs</a><